WEBVTT

03:10.774 --> 03:12.941
The boy who died was the son
of an Inspector General.

03:13.714 --> 03:15.172
They will tear our family apart.

03:15.858 --> 03:17.358
Our daughter's future is at stake...

03:23.108 --> 03:25.274
I'm scared of going to jail.

03:25.816 --> 03:27.108
You? Going to jail?

03:27.483 --> 03:28.733
Not while your father is alive.
